The tutorial focuses on the challenges and techniques for ensuring safety and reliability in machine learning, which are central topics in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The tutorial also discusses the potential risks and vulnerabilities of machine learning systems, which are relevant to the subfield of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the tutorial covers methods for testing and verifying machine learning models, which are important in software engineering (cs.SE) and control systems (cs.SY).
